{"tid":1352163,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"叫人唔好理元朗就係五毛","createTime":"2019-07-22T17:43:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T17:49:01.000Z","uid":203508,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3d776d4d13e5b24cccf162fd589b75a32331cd91","tid":1352163,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:43:45.000Z","msg":"你先係五毛 又叫人含撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又爭取回應五大訴求<br />\n又叫人感化藍絲廢老<br />\n又叫人返屋企<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">叫人做啲無用既野 等有更多人犧牲</span></span><br />\n根本成個連登都係五毛 一個有用既po都凝聚唔到<br />\n共産黨已經<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">買撚起左成個政府 買撚埋軍隊 法官 仲買撚埋成個元朗</span></span><br />\n沙田一役對港人的<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">種族清洗</span></span>已開始 元朗一未開打就無左 成為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">深圳市元朗街道</span></span><br />\n請對準政權<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">CCCP 中国共産黨</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f38dce8d546f7381a08c89b67eb7ad6ac1f8ed","tid":1352163,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:44:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"589552e41150884f6a678b1459dc1c5c6725f299","tid":1352163,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:44:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f8d4e8a90e14b480aa4e4cc31155473a71786b","tid":1352163,"uid"